$$
Q=\left(
\begin{array}{cccc}
 \frac{1}{f_x} & 0 & 0 & -\frac{c_x}{f_x} \\
 0 & \frac{1}{f_y} & 0 & -\frac{c_y}{f_y} \\
 0 & 0 & 0 & 1 \\
 0 & 0 & \frac{1}{L f_x} & 0 \\
\end{array}
\right) = 
\left(
\begin{array}{cccc}
 f_x & 0 & c_x & 0 \\
 0 & f_y & c_y & 0 \\
 0 & 0 & 0 & L f_x \\
 0 & 0 & 1 & 0 \\
\end{array}
\right)^{-1}
$$